       I’m  bg fn f tmtn: gttng tchnlgy t d thngs fr y. It’s th wy f th ftr, ftr ll, sn’t t?
      </p>
      <p>
       Why cpy n rtcl by hnd svrl tms whn y cn cpy nd pst n th cmptr nd hv t snd t  thsnd cps? Why g t th bnk t mk  bll pymnt whn y cn hv yr nln bnk ccnt tmtclly snd t th pymnt? Why wsh nd dry clths by hnd whn mchns cn d t?
      </p>
      <p>
       And whl I m nt gng t dvct thrwng t ll tchnlgy nd tmtn, I wll mk  cs fr “n-tmtn” n sm css.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mkng thngs hrdr sn’t  bd thng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Whn w mst d thngs rslvs, nd t csts s n tm nd ffrt, t frcs s t cnsdr whthr t’s wrth dng t ll.
      </p>
      <p>
       Whn y hv t wlk t  str (r drv) nd by smthng wth csh, t’s lss cnvnnt thn rdrng t nln nd hvng t dlvrd t yr dr. Bt tht ncnvnnc s  cst, nd ths hghr cst wll gv s ps.
      </p>
      <p>
       And tht ps s vrythng. Thr s nfnty n  ps. Wthn tht ps s thght, s  dcsn tht w mst mk,  dcsn w hv slly tmtd bcs th ctn s s sy nd fst tht w dn’t nd t thnk bt t.
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s sy t by thngs — sr thn vr bfr. It’s sy t cnsm nfrmtn, s mch nfrmtn tht w frgt bt crtng nd bldng. It’s sy t cmmnct, s mch s tht w cmmnct n mr wys nd mr ftn thn w sd t. It’s sy t cqr nd crt chttr … bt shld t b?
      </p>
      <p>
       Ths s wht w nd t tk ps t cnsdr. Thngs r sy, bt s tht th wy w wnt thm? Esy s nc, bt t lds t cnsqncs tht w mght nt wnt. It lds t xcss, t dbt, t nfrmtn vrld, t gttng ft, t hvng t mch, t nvr hvng ngh tm fr wht’s trly mprtnt.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mnmlsm, s I’v sd bfr, s th nswr. Rdc, d nd hv lss.
      </p>
      <p>
       Un-tmtn s  pth t mnmlsm.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hr r jst  fw xmpls t gt s thnkng:
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        Ck yr fd, nstd f byng fst fd r mcrwvbl r thr pr-prprd fd. Y’ll t lss nd t’ll b hlthr. I’d sggst w grw r wn fd (r kll t f y’r  mt tr), bt w my nt b rdy fr tht knd f dvncd tchnlgy yt.
       </li>
       <li>
        Hnd cd wbsts nd blg psts. It’s vry sy t s sftwr, sch s Drmwvr, t cd  st. Or Txtmt r
        <span class="caps">
