        </span>
        dt t cd  pg r wrt sftwr. Or blg sftwr sch s WrdPrss r Tmblr r th lk t crt nd wrt  blg. Bt wht f y hd t cd vrythng by hnd, n  txt dtr sch s Txtdt r Ntpd? Y’d b frcd t bld lss, t wrt lss, t cnsdr vry wrd nd vry pg nd vry st, nd dcd whthr t’s wrth dng. Sm thng wth sftwr cd: y’d wrt lss, nd mk vry ln cnt.
       </li>
