        Wlk t by, r drv f tht’s nt pssbl. If y hv strs wthn wlkng dstnc (r bkng dstnc), frc yrslf t s yr lgs nd s csh nstd f  crdt crd r chck, n rdr t by smthng. Y’ll gv t  scnd nd thrd thght, bcs s th tm wrth th ffrt?
